@page "/"

<div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h1 class="mb-4">📊 Data Crunch Agent</h1>

        <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">What is this?</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    A <strong>Microsoft Foundry hosted agent</strong> that analyzes your CSV data using real C# code.
                    Upload a file, and the agent will parse it, compute statistics, and detect outliers — all powered
                    by function tools running server-side.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-primary">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h1>📋</h1>
                        <h6>Parse Data</h6>
                        <small class="text-muted">Detect columns, count rows, preview data</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-success">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h1>📈</h1>
                        <h6>Compute Statistics</h6>
                        <small class="text-muted">Mean, median, std dev, percentiles</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-warning">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h1>🔍</h1>
                        <h6>Detect Outliers</h6>
                        <small class="text-muted">IQR method with statistical fences</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
            <a href="/analyze" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                🚀 Start Analyzing
            </a>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-4" />

        <h5>How It Works</h5>
        <pre class="bg-light p-3 rounded"><code>Upload CSV → Agent parses data → Computes statistics → Detects outliers → Returns narrative</code></pre>
        <p class="text-muted small">
            The agent uses <code>gpt-5-mini</code> to orchestrate three C# function tools.
            All computation happens server-side — the model decides which tools to call, but the math is real code.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
